text: Come home to cozy Rockport, nestled in the Skagit River Valley. Home has two bedrooms and bonus space, plus a covered porch, all on a neatly maintained corner lot. 12 minutes from Concrete, 45 minutes to Burlington. Towards the north is the North Cascades National Park; the Sauk Mountain trailhead is less than 10 miles away; Baker Lake less than 30.

Discover the quintessential Pacific Northwest luxury beach retreat on the Bay. This expansive property features soaring beamed ceilings that start outside & carry to the inside. A magnificent massive fireplace in the main living area creates a warm & inviting atmosphere of rustic charm & elegance. The spacious lower level recreation room & stunning wine cellar offer more space for relaxing & entertaining. The outdoor amenities are endless with a tennis/pickleball court, putting green, fire pit and a voluminous deck with built-in outdoor kitchen. The 143 feet of beachfront is perfect for relaxing, heading out for a paddle, or building beach forts with the driftwood. Create cherished memories for decades to come in this one of a kind estate.

Light, bright & airy Creekside neighborhood retreat positioned on the corner. As you enter from the covered deck to inside-natural light floods every room, enhanced by vaulted ceilings & skylights. Spacious living room offers cozy fireplace, dining area, surrounded by larger windows giving views of Fidalgo Bay, Mt. Baker, lush community landscaping/greenbelt & back deck access. Open kitchen features newer paint, refinished cabinets, quartz counter, breakfast nook, garden window with views. The primary suite includes vaulted ceilings, perfectly situated for the views, ensuite 3/4 bath & walk-in closet. Finishing out the home are 2 addtl bedrooms, full bath, laundry room & 2car garage with more storage under home + community RV/Boat parking.

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Old Town Anacortes, this property offers unparalleled convenience. Imagine strolling to charming shops, savoring meals at local eateries, and soaking in the waterfront ambianceall just steps from your doorstep. With festivals and events adding to the lively atmosphere, every day brings new adventures. While the existing small home is sold as is, the true treasure lies in the land and its prime location. Build your dream home or consider building brand new with a MIL or ADU and embrace the lifestyle that celebrates the essence of Anacortes.

This home is in mint condition! Fresh paint throughout including doors, trim, etc. Located in Rockridge with a partial view, corner lot, dead end street, right next to Anacortes Forest Land Trails. 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, custom blinds throughout, very sweet front porch, nice size backyard plus a nice shed. The open concept kitchen offers stainless appliances, granite counters, lots of cabinetry too. Family room offers a fireplace and built in cabinets/shelving. The formal living is very bright open to the formal dining - perfect for entertaining.

Welcome to the Marcella Court Cul-De-Sac! Here is where you will find this charming 2-bedroom, 1.5- bath HOME. This property boasts an amazing GARDEN SPACE with established fruiting plants, PERFECT for green thumbs and enthusiasts. The kitchen, living room, and dining are OPEN & BRIGHT. The unfinished BONUS ROOM offers potential for customization, whether you choose to convert it back into a garage or create a space that suits your needs. While the HOME requires a little cosmetic work, it presents a FANTASTIC OPPORTUNITY to personalize and MAKE IT YOUR OWN.

This beautifully updated and meticulously maintained home is situated on a spacious lot in an ideal location, complete with a large detached garage and convenient alley access. Abundant natural light fills the home, complementing the tall ceilings, expansive living room, and generously sized bedrooms. The living room seamlessly connects to a spacious kitchen, which leads to a large storage room with a door to the outside to a large fully fenced backyard. Recent upgrades include a new furnace, water heater, carpet, LVP flooring, a modern kitchen with new appliances, and a newly built garage etc. This is a picture perfect home that offers a wonderful setting and ample amount of parking. All the big items have been taken care of for you!

Welcome to your dream home in Birdsview! This stunning 2018-built 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers modern amenities on just over an acre of land. The open concept layout features a spacious kitchen with white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy meals in the breakfast nook or the large dining room. Huge windows and an oversized sliding door lead to a deck, covered patio with hot tub and expansive yard, perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom boasts its own deck and a luxurious 5-piece bath with a soaking tub and double sinks. Newer heat pump and whole home generator provide peace of mind in any season. Experience comfort and style in this beautiful home! Schedule your private tour today!

9+ acre gated entry property with upscale custom home, ADU, barn, shop, garages, pasture, garden space, pond, private walking trails, and space to build - this one has it all! The main home features two stories plus a fully finished daylight basement, vaulted ceilings, skylights and ample windows to take advantage of the natural light, hardwood floors, Chef's kitchen, wet bar, hydronic radiant heat throughout. Enjoy the spacious, open plan 2 bed/1 bath ADU as a hobby space, guest house, or rent it out for additional income. Bring your animals, toys, RV, boat, and friends; there is space for everything and everyone! Home is adjacent to public land for additional privacy.

Fantastic opportunity to own an affordable condo in a wonderful location right in the heart of Mount Vernon. Enjoy easy living in this 3rd floor 2 bedroom unit. With brand new interior paint & some recent cosmetic upgrades makes this a move-in-ready opportunity. The spacious floor plan features a galley kitchen with upgraded stainless appliances, new tile floors, countertops, and backsplash. Nice dining area open to the large living room with a fireplace. A wall of windows with a sliding glass door opens up to the big covered deck that is very private with beautiful territorial views. 1 covered parking space & 1 uncovered. This well maintained building has a secured entrance and an elevator. Close to shopping, schools, hospital, & more!

Come check out this beautifully maintained 3BD 2BA manufactured home on the hill in Clear Lake! The home is in excellent condition, sitting on a full slab with a block foundation. Relocated to this site in 2005 by its original owner, it now enjoys the stability of a permanent foundation. Upgrades include newer windows, roof, siding, and plumbing. With a newer detached 18x24 garage/shop and a foundation ready for a stick-framed garage, this home offers convenience and potential. Best of all, you can take a leisurely walk to the lake, making it perfect for those who love the tranquility of waterside living. Don't miss this opportunity to own a delightful home in an idyllic location!

Turnkey waterfront home offers 77 of water-frontage on level, sunny lot to enjoy year-round lake fun. Private back patio greets you as you enter the fenced yard & charming low maintenance home. Vaulted ceilings soar w/natural light. Slate flooring everywhere & water facing Chefs kitchen w/granite & Viking appliances. Walk up a few stairs to primary w/spa-like shower, 2nd bdr & bonus loft w/view. Large deck faces lush lawn to waters edge for low bank access. Deep-water dock, for boat & all water sports. Spectacular home offers plenty of parking for all your guests. Newer roof, paint, windows & extra storage for all your water-toys. 5 minutes to all amenities & to Historic DT Mt Vernon for fine dining. Just off HWY 9 and 7 Minutes to I-5.

Country living with beautiful territorial and mountain views. This spacious home offers quality finishes with solid wood doors, gorgeous cabinets & massive storage! Step out onto a private deck and view beautiful terraced gardens & total privacy for relaxation. Separate 907 sq. ft. Mother-in-law unit below with private access, master suite, walk-in closet, full kitchen, dining and living room. Perfect guest quarters or possible additional income. Approx. 1.43 acres offering a beautiful wooded section, huge garden location, fenced chicken coop & run. 832 sq. ft. garage with a wood stove, storage, separate shop area. Detached 40' by 26' RV garage/shop.

Well-maintained 3 bedrooms, 2 bathroom rambler with many great features, including central AC!. Enjoy the beautiful PNW summers with a cool house. This house has a newer roof, interior paint, and a newly remodeled primary bathroom. LVP flooring throughout most of the house with carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen has all appliances plus a nice-sized deck off the dining nook. Fully fenced backyard and 2-car garage. Storage galore with a full-size, walk-in crawl space, the access is in back of the house. Backs up to a city walking trail, allowing for privacy in the backyard with no neighbors directly behind you. The covered front porch overlooks the nicely landscaped front yard. There is additional parking in the neighborhood for guests.

Discover the perfect blend of charm and opportunity with this recently remodeled 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom shop apartment on a stunning 8.6-acre parcel. Live comfortably in this adorable home while you build your dream house, or simply enjoy the serene lifestyle it offers. The property includes ownership of the iconic Big Rock and presents an excellent opportunity for a home-based business in a highly desirable location. Enjoy the tranquility of this peaceful retreat, just moments from town. Don't miss out on this unique and versatile property!

Offered here is a wonderful Skyline lot ready for your immediate custom home building plans, close to the Marina and Tug Boat Park, cabana, Clubhouse and the tennis courts. At 7841 square feet, there's enough room for your dream home. The lot has a slight uphill grade allowing for great western exposure to include gorgeous sunsets. Water, sewer and power are all in the street. There's not very many of these vacant lots left in Skyline!

This recently updated, well maintained and cozy cottage located close to the newly revived and bustling downtown of Mount Vernon will surely impress. One car garage with workshop space and extra storage is simply the cherry on top. Eat in kitchen features granite countertops and newer stainless appliances. Attic and crawl space have been recently upgraded with extra insulation and sealing to improve the homes efficiency and exterior noise reduction. You'll be pleasantly surprised by this home.

{ COVETED TINAS COMA Neighborhood } Breathtaking panoramic views of the Majestic Cascade Mountains & Skagit River. As you step inside, an abundance of natural light flows through the rooms. The kitchen, featuring granite countertops, overlooks the space, creating a seamless area for cooking & casual gatherings w/ the grand views from all windows // Retreat to the luxurious owners suite, complete w/walk-in closet & spa-like bath // The expansive basement is a car enthusiasts dream, providing parking for up to 5 add vehicles/toys & offers plenty of storage space for all your needs w/ it's own separate driveway & could be easily converted to a finished basement // Outside, enjoy the beautiful Trex like deck to soak in the spectacular views!

Discover this timeless rambler, perfectly situated just moments from downtown, Skagit Valley Hospital, shopping, dining, and numerous parks. Recently refreshed, this home is filled with natural light and exudes nostalgic charm. Its open layout and midcentury design elements offer a seamless blend of vintage appeal and contemporary comfort. From the dining room, French doors open to a spacious patio and a gracious backyard, perfect for entertaining. Mature fruit trees and a dedicated garden plot enhance the outdoor experience. A beautiful home in a highly desirable neighborhood makes this the perfect place to call home. Embrace the beauty and tranquility of life in Skagit Valley. Come make this very special place your own.

Discover your dream home in Shelter Bay! This fee simple, single-level gem is nestled in a private cul-de-sac and surrounded by a greenbelt. Enjoy the community pool, clubhouse, tennis/pickleball courts, golf course and two private beaches. For avid boaters, a concrete boat ramp provides easy access to the stunning San Juan Islands. The home features a large yard, composite deck and mature gardens, perfect for outdoor living. Dont miss this unique opportunity to enjoy vibrant community amenities and the natural beauty of the Pacific Northwest. Experience the best of FEE SIMPLE Shelter Bay living today!
